FAQ App Coding Plan

1. Setup
- Provide basic SwiftUI project targeting iOS 17.
- Store small preferences using `LocalDataStore`.
- Bundle a `Resources/FAQItems.json` file.

2. Onboarding
- Simple introduction screen shown on first launch.
- Persist completion in `UserDefaults`.

3. Help Section
- `FAQItem` model and `FAQStore` for loading JSON data.
- `HelpHomeView` lists categories of FAQ items.
- `FAQListView` shows questions per category with search.
- `FAQDetailView` displays answers.

4. Tests
- Unit test verifying FAQ data loads from the bundle.

Future improvements may include remote content updates and a contact form.
